overview: Seok-yong, who is one of the most famous generals in the village, is trying to find medicine for his mother's illness, but is deceived by Lee Young-gam and puts pressure on the innocent Si clan. Seok-yong, unable to tolerate injustice, goes out to find out the truth from Young-gam Lee, but is framed for murder and imprisoned in prison.
title: Death Wrestle
